() Tj
T* (5.1 COMMAND INTERFACE) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Supported commands:) Tj
T* (• simulate: run one profile + workload scenario.) Tj
T* (• compare: run multiple hardware profiles against the same workload \(requires at least two --hw) Tj
T* (entries\).) Tj
T* (• save: write current hardware/workload setup to key=value file.) Tj
T* (• help: usage guidance.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Input style supports both --flag value and --flag=value.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (5.2 HARDWARE CONFIGURATION MODEL) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (HardwareConfig includes:) Tj
T* (• cpu_cores \(int\)) Tj
T* (• ram_gb \(double\)) Tj
T* (• storage \(HDD | SSD | NVMe\)) Tj
T* (• network_mbps \(double\)) Tj
T* (• optional label) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Default baseline is 4 cores, 8 GiB RAM, SSD, 100 Mb/s.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (5.3 WORKLOAD MODEL) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (WorkloadSpec includes:) Tj
T* (• task_type \(e.g., rendering, compiling, database, streaming, generic\)) Tj
T* (• complexity \(Low, Medium, High\)) Tj
T* (• task_size \(double scalar\)) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Each task maps to heuristic weights \(cpu, mem_per_size, io, net\) for simulation.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (5.4 SIMULATION ALGORITHM) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (The simulation computes three core time components:) Tj
T* (1. Compute component: inversely scaled by cores^0.72 \(sub-linear parallelism\).) Tj
T* (2. I/O component: scaled by storage latency factor \(HDD slower, NVMe faster\).) Tj
T* (3. Network component: scaled against a 500 Mb/s reference.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Total execution estimate combines dominant and average effects:) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (execution_time = 0.65 * dominant_component + 0.35 * average\(component_sum\)) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Memory pressure penalty is applied when modeled memory requirement exceeds configured RAM.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (5.5 BOTTLENECK ANALYSIS LOGIC) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (After simulation, the profiler:) Tj
ET
endstream
endobj
